snippet.title: PENTHOS - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
PENTHOS is an original, full-length visual novel by Cruelhouse, releasing October 16th as freeware for Windows, Mac, and Linux. 

For more, check out our 
website: https://www.cruelhouse.com/
